{
  "info": {
    "name": "Right Code - Image Generation",
    "description": "Right Code 图片生成 API 集合\n\n基础地址：https://www.right.codes/draw\n接口：POST /v1/images/generations",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{api_key}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "生成图片",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/images/generations",
          "host": [
            "{{base_url}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "v1",
            "images",
            "generations"
          ]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"model\": \"{{model}}\",\n  \"prompt\": \"生成一张边牧与古牧正在抖音直播间直播带货截图\",\n  \"image\": [\"{{image_base64}}\"],\n  \"size\": \"{{size}}\",\n  \"response_format\": \"url\"\n}"
        },
        "description": "调用 Right Code 图片生成接口，返回生成图片的直链。\n\n### 传参考图（两种方式）\n\n**方式一（推荐，通用）** — 直接用命令行生成 base64 后粘贴：\n```bash\n# Windows PowerShell\n[Convert]::ToBase64String([IO.File]::ReadAllBytes(\"C:\\path\\to\\image.png\"))\n\n# macOS / Linux\nbase64 -i /path/to/image.png\n```\n把输出的字符串前面加上 `data:image/png;base64,`，粘贴到环境变量 `image_base64` 中即可。\n\n**方式二** — Postman v11+ 桌面端自动读取：\n在环境变量 `image_path` 中填写本地图片的绝对路径，Pre-request Script 会自动转换。\n\n**不需要参考图时**：把 `image_base64` 和 `image_path` 都留空即可。",
        "event": [
          {
            "listen": "prerequest",
            "script": {
              "exec": [
                "const imagePath = pm.environment.get(\"image_path\");",
                "if (imagePath && imagePath.trim() !== \"\") {",
                "    if (pm.fs && typeof pm.fs.readFile === \"function\") {",
                "        const bytes = new Uint8Array(pm.fs.readFile(imagePath));",
                "        let binary = \"\";",
                "        for (let i = 0; i < bytes.length; i++) {",
                "            binary += String.fromCharCode(bytes[i]);",
                "        }",
                "        pm.environment.set(\"image_base64\", `data:image/png;base64,${btoa(binary)}`);",
                "        console.log(`已读取参考图: ${imagePath}`);",
                "    } else {",
                "        console.warn(\"pm.fs 不可用，请直接将 base64 填入 image_base64 变量（方法见请求描述）\");",
                "    }",
                "}",
                ""
              ],
              "type": "text/javascript"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "response": [
        {
          "name": "成功示例",
          "status": "OK",
          "code": 200,
          "header": [
            {
              "key": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ],
          "body": "{\n  \"created\": 1777689832,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://file4.aitohumanize.com/file/dfa13fe60e7649e88f46037b968b54a3.png\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"usage\": {\n    \"total_tokens\": 6267,\n    \"input_tokens\": 17,\n    \"output_tokens\": 6250\n  }\n}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
